01:54.000 --> 02:01.800
Also, white onion has extra water, so you are going to be cooking this and stewing it and simmering it for a long time, for many hours.

02:01.900 --> 02:10.473
So, you want to make sure that you get an onion that one, has a lot of flavor, and then number two, it also doesn't release a lot of water.

02:11.200 --> 02:19.200
I prefer to chop it up into finer chops, but it's up to you if you want to chop it into bigger pieces

02:19.500 --> 02:25.800
